title: Ebro In The Morning - Tiffany Cabàn talks Rikers + Guest - Lakeyah
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Milwaukee rapper Lakeyah sits down with Ebro in the Morning alongside Quality Control's CEO Pierre “Pee” Thomas to discuss what makes her stand out as an MC.

New York's Democratic Nominee for NYC Council District 22, Tiffany Cabàn sat down with Ebro in the Morning to discussed very bad conditions she experienced during her visit at Rikers. 

Ebro In The Morning is hosted by Ebro, Laura Stylez, and Rosenberg.
